{"tid":1565481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不死重生】中国網紅挖洞埋「香港加油」許願牌　日本人神社尋回","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T19:02:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":85,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"235f30084d33465d2d69eda59de7e33cf5cae6a5","tid":1565481,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"中国人往大阪神社偷拔「支持香港」許願牌丟棄  日本人憤怒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559651</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2450000/2450842/jp_thumb_20190913_S_v2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2450000%2F2450842%2Fjp_thumb_20190913_S_v2_1024.jpg&h=a6dd5489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反修例運動至今已3個月，香港各區設有連儂牆讓市民寫下心聲，亦有市民到日本旅遊時會利用許願牌（繪馬）寫下「香港加油」等字句，卻屢屢受到他人破壞。內地一名網紅到訪大阪某神社時，就拆下兩塊香港人所寫的許願牌，更將它們埋在土中，有日本人拾回，令許願牌重見天日。<br />\n<br />\n一名內地網紅「樊燁燁燁」將寫下「香港加油」等字句的許願牌拆下，更埋個一個偏僻的角落，事件被翻譯成日文之後在Twitter瘋傳，惹起網民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n一名熱愛日本文化的香港人得知此事後，特意在Google Map中嘗試找出隱藏的地點，並請一位日本朋友到場幫忙尋找。想不到網民所找的京都八坂神社，真的是內地網紅埋下許願牌的地方，讓日本朋友順利找到香港人所寫的許願牌。另外又有人貼出一名神官（日本神職人員）將許願牌重新掛起的照片。<br />\n<br />\n事源一名微博有13萬粉絲的內地網紅，本月6日大阪某神社時將兩名香港人的許願牌拆下，更在微博上發帖指該名香港人的願望實現不了，又寫「誰都不許說我大中國不好」等句子並與網民對罵。有日本網民認為此舉已是「褻瀆神明」甚至盜竊，又指「如果你到另一個國家，就應該尊重該國的傳統和文化」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2450842/%E3%80%90%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%8B%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A5%E3%80%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E6%8C%96%E6%B4%9E%E5%9F%8B%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9%E3%80%8D%E8%A8%B1%E9%A1%98%E7%89%8C%E3%80%80%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B0%E7%A5%9E%E7%A4%BE%E5%B0%8B%E5%9B%9E?mtc=10012</code></pre>"},{"pid":"618a30202662e7bb49fd1c65488b19e024cfbb47","tid":1565481,"uid":255816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"【行動po】全民文宣日！每星期一齊貼連儂貼文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思借個位宣傳<br />\n小妹提議每星期一四晚做全民文宣<br />\n一齊出街貼連儂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa6b4b81f40088bbdd56044f9384114acf37b7a","tid":1565481,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7b46e368212c64a3c891c1fbdfe3e7da1b31e9","tid":1565481,"uid":284304,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:18:48.000Z","msg":"日本人真係世界第一"},{"pid":"6ae12516eb0312a883e3d73e92a2c36741e9c696","tid":1565481,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccFUCqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccFUCqw.jpg&h=f44c3870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de667b7973aeabd0e315a12960fe99cde8302c4c","tid":1565481,"uid":37524,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"神聖之物都敢玩<br />\n呢條閪女人一定會有報應"},{"pid":"302c30b1924e5a2484f09b78c645698c306f11cd","tid":1565481,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>正視聽，假消防嘅推論係立足於流料上</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565045</a>"},{"pid":"eddeaa81bd710201435de4c0ac2945897b30fdee","tid":1565481,"uid":43600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天有眼"},{"pid":"a42e79b1881f2b98a2d21b7f53a15398f5de9ede","tid":1